      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form uncertainty documentation at a qualitative level is sufficient at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "The power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen et al.) is acknowledged as an approximation. Sensitivity to model form is noted qualitatively; formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2 and has not been performed."
    },
