      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameter documentation at nominal values is sufficient at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity, density, and hemolysis model coefficients are set to nominal published values. Formal input uncertainty propagation is not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
